  │ │                                                                                            │ │  
  │ │                                                   
  
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
  
  # Before you execute:
  ---------------------------
  make install
  ---------------------------
  
  # Run:
  ---------------------------
  make menuconfig 
  ---------------------------
  
  Remove the [*] from  [ ] Enable loadable module support  ----  
  ----------------------------------------
  [ ] Enable loadable module support  ----  
  ----------------------------------------
  
  Run:
  ----------------------------------------
  make install
  ----------------------------------------
  
  
